 poético de asombrosa armonía, tejiendo todos los hilos sin perder nunca el control, con una complejidad que convive con la claridad de modo admirable.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 4aHistoria y crítica de la literatura / Literatura en español / Siglo de Oro - XVI-XVII / España /. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / Spanish & Portuguese.2bisacsh1 ade Arellano, Ignacio, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary Studies 2023z9783111318264oZDB-23-DSP40uhttps://doi.org/10.31819/978396869366840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783968693668423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783968693668/original  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DSPb2023